up files must be put into the import directory (e.g. by ftp). If, additionally, the webserver can write to this directory, Lodel will offer to store backups there (backup.php). This directory is, therefore, very useful for large sites.','en','install',2,20050513172237),(5428,'howto_index_type_1','Tag and style must contain only non-accented letters and numbers','en','admin',2,20050428223138),(5429,'howto_index_type_2','The style defined in the text-processing program\'s Document Model may contain accented characters and spaces. Accents and spaces will be automatically removed. For example, the style \"Keyword\" in the Document Model, must be defined as \"Keyword\" here','en','admin',2,20050429102931),(5430,'howto_index_type_3','\"Style\" may also indicate language. If this is the case, each style must be followed by \":\" and the language code. Furthermore, the styles must be separated by a comma. Example: motcle:fr, keywords:en.','en','admin',2,20050429102931),(5431,'howto_indivdual_type_1','(*) Styles and tags may only contain non-accented characters and numbers','en','admin',2,20050429102931),(5432,'howto_indivdual_type_2','The style defined in the text-processing program\'s Document Model may contain accented characters and spaces. Accents and spaces will be automatically removed.','en','admin',2,20050429102931),(6634,'error_contacting_servoo',NULL,'ar','error',1,20050429104359),(5433,'howto_indivdual_type_3','For example the style \"Keyword\" in the Document Model, must be defined as \"Keyword\" here','en','admin',2,20050429102931),(5434,'howto_install_servoo_on_private_server','You can install your own ServOO server : this requires installation of OpenOffice.org and Java on your server. Such an installation requires a dedicated server securely set up. ServOO is (will be) distributed in a separate package from Lodel from <a href=\"http://sourceforge.net/projects/lodel/\" target=\"_new\">http://sourceforge.net/projects/lodel/</a>. When ServOO is installed, enter teh connection parameters below. If you are installing a ServOO server, we would encourage you to make it publicly available and to register it at <a href=\"http://www.lodel.org/\" target=\"_new\">http://www.lodel.org</a>.','en','install',2,20050513154951),(5435,'howto_littletexts','@howto_littletexts','en','lodeladmin',1,20050421173650),(5436,'howto_me','Additional information','en','admin',2,20050513164417),(5437,'howto_move','Click on the publication into which you wish to move your document','en','edition',2,20050428112635),(5438,'howto_name_website','without accents, spaces, or special characters','en','lodeladmin',2,20050421173650),(5439,'howto_on_scripts_extensions_choose_php_or_html_extensions','Lodel scripts are PHP scripts, and it is recommended that you use the extension \".php\". However, if you wish, it is possible to choose the extension \".html\". This option is not recommended : it requires  in particular special configuration of the server (i.e. that html files be parsed by php).','en','install',2,20050513154421),(5440,'howto_parameters_mysql_create_database','Please check that the database access rights are set correctly, that MySQL user %s is entitled to create a new database (the majority of providers do not allow this) or begin the installation process afresh.','en','lodeladmin',2,20050421181031),(5441,'howto_symbolic_links_in_lodel','If your webserver supports symbolic links, certain files can be linked rather than copied. Linking allows more flexible management of updates, access rights, etc. This is only warranted <strong>if Lodel is managing several sites</strong>. It is necessary, if that is not done, to configure the webserver to \"follow symbolic links\" which is generally considered less secure. Please consult your webserver\'s software documentation (e.g., Apache).','en','install',2,20050513152755),(5442,'identification','Identification','en','common',2,20050503182033),(5443,'identifier','Identifier','en','edition',2,20050428112635),(5